text: "I Still Miss Someone" is a 1958 song by Johnny Cash. It was taken from his second studio album The Fabulous Johnny Cash. It was the B-side to his single Don't Take Your Guns to Town. The Highwaymen covered it live in 1990. It has covered by number of singers over the years including the duet by Martina McBride featuring Dolly Parton.
